1
00:00:08,550 --> 00:00:12,262
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>And in weird things in space news,
that mysterious "rift" is still there.</i></font>

2
00:00:12,346 --> 00:00:16,475
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Not gone yet. You remember that, don't you?
It's probably important. Back to you, Tabitha.</i></font>

3
00:00:16,558 --> 00:00:19,811
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick, Mom's working, and Dad's still sleeping.
I'm gonna be late.</font>

4
00:00:19,895 --> 00:00:22,356
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, yeah. [burps] I got you. Here.</font>

5
00:00:22,439 --> 00:00:25,776
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Holy shit. ls the portal gun working again?
- Yeah, pretty much.</font>

6
00:00:26,652 --> 00:00:27,653
<font face="Serif" size="18">[roaring]</font>

7
00:00:27,736 --> 00:00:29,279
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sometimes that happens.</font>

8
00:00:32,533 --> 00:00:34,618
<font face="Serif" size="18">Just get the keys.</font>

9
00:00:36,245 --> 00:00:39,081
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's actually been nice taking a break
from the portal travel stuff.</font>

10
00:00:39,164 --> 00:00:41,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've been racking up a lot
of high school adventures.</font>

11
00:00:41,583 --> 00:00:43,293
<font face="Serif" size="18">I have a process, Morty.</font>

12
00:00:43,377 --> 00:00:46,922
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm fixing my portal gun, and every time
you bring it up, it blocks my creative flow.</font>

13
00:00:47,005 --> 00:00:50,467
<font face="Serif" size="18">And then I'm forced to take longer on purpose
just to train you to not bring it up.</font>

14
00:00:50,551 --> 00:00:52,219
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jeez. Do you know what "projection" is?</font>

15
00:00:52,302 --> 00:00:55,305
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Do you?
- No. I heard Mom use it.</font>

16
00:00:55,389 --> 00:00:56,473
<font face="Serif" size="18">[school bell rings]</font>

17
00:00:56,557 --> 00:00:59,601
<font face="Serif" size="18">Lord, no. He's here again?
Morty protocol, children.</font>

18
00:00:59,685 --> 00:01:04,982
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, what's it now? Brain bugs? Space worms?
Have I been <i>The Faculty'd</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> again?</font>

19
00:01:05,065 --> 00:01:07,109
<font face="Serif" size="18">You don't have to react like this every day.</font>

20
00:01:07,192 --> 00:01:10,487
<font face="Serif" size="18">Last time, the aliens made me lick
all the toilet seats.</font>

21
00:01:10,571 --> 00:01:13,282
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's right, made me.
I see that look on your faces.</font>

22
00:01:13,365 --> 00:01:14,408
<font face="Serif" size="18">[building rumbling]</font>

23
00:01:14,491 --> 00:01:17,786
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What did you do, you tiny monster?
- This isn't me.</font>

24
00:01:25,043 --> 00:01:28,964
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>The people demand to know.
Do these visitors come in peace?</i></font>

25
00:01:29,047 --> 00:01:33,260
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>But first, "Peter's Pizza Corner. "
What slice we reviewing today, Petey?</i></font>

26
00:01:33,343 --> 00:01:34,428
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Cheese.</i></font>

27
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:43,228
<font face="Serif" size="18">If these aliens want Earth,
they'll have to go through Egypt.</font>

28
00:01:43,312 --> 00:01:45,856
<font face="Serif" size="18">And they can ask mummies how that goes.</font>

29
00:01:48,609 --> 00:01:50,444
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mummy mia!</font>

30
00:01:56,908 --> 00:01:58,869
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dinosaurs are back?</font>

31
00:01:58,952 --> 00:02:01,038
<font face="Serif" size="18">Monkeys went bald?</font>

32
00:02:01,580 --> 00:02:02,956
<font face="Serif" size="18">[theme music playing]</font>

33
00:02:39,284 --> 00:02:43,288
<font face="Serif" size="18">Before we start, where are the rest of us?</font>

34
00:02:43,997 --> 00:02:44,956
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh...</font>

35
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:47,834
<font face="Serif" size="18">They died. Long time ago.</font>

36
00:02:47,918 --> 00:02:50,796
<font face="Serif" size="18">Way before us. We didn't see nothing.</font>

37
00:02:50,879 --> 00:02:54,549
<font face="Serif" size="18">But surely our ancestors must have left
some evidence behind.</font>

38
00:02:56,385 --> 00:02:57,469
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why is he nervous?</font>

39
00:02:59,638 --> 00:03:03,350
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because you're dinosaurs.</font>

40
00:03:03,433 --> 00:03:06,228
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's weird. Thought you were dead.</font>

41
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:11,775
<font face="Serif" size="18">Moving on, we "dinosaurs"
evolved here on Earth</font>

42
00:03:11,858 --> 00:03:14,695
<font face="Serif" size="18">until our technology was Planetarily harmonic.</font>

43
00:03:14,778 --> 00:03:17,739
<font face="Serif" size="18">That being the goal with technology.</font>

44
00:03:18,532 --> 00:03:21,159
<font face="Serif" size="18">After we achieved perfect balance
with Mother Earth,</font>

45
00:03:21,243 --> 00:03:24,496
<font face="Serif" size="18">our best and bravest left to help other planets.</font>

46
00:03:24,579 --> 00:03:28,542
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Over millions of years, we've called
many worlds home and helped each one flourish.</i></font>

47
00:03:28,625 --> 00:03:33,171
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Imagine our surprise upon returning home
to find our species extinct</i></font>

48
00:03:33,255 --> 00:03:35,632
<font face="Serif" size="18">and Earth now in the care of...</font>

49
00:03:35,716 --> 00:03:36,925
<font face="Serif" size="18">you guys.</font>

50
00:03:37,008 --> 00:03:39,803
<font face="Serif" size="18">When we left, you were basically squirrels.</font>

51
00:03:39,886 --> 00:03:44,641
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, we've come a long way,
and we've buried a lot more than nuts.</font>

52
00:03:44,725 --> 00:03:49,312
<font face="Serif" size="18">We've evolved past nonconstructive criticism,
so let's agree you've done your best.</font>

53
00:03:49,396 --> 00:03:50,313
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're still alive.</font>

54
00:03:50,397 --> 00:03:55,402
<font face="Serif" size="18">But surely there was some point between
gunpowder and something called Amazon Prime</font>

55
00:03:55,485 --> 00:03:58,572
<font face="Serif" size="18">that you folks had to think,
"Are we supposed to be running a planet?</font>

56
00:03:58,655 --> 00:04:02,367
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wouldn't we rather make Marvel movies?"
How many Marvel movies have you made?</font>

57
00:04:02,451 --> 00:04:04,369
<font face="Serif" size="18">Twenty-nine, and 14 more on the way.</font>

58
00:04:04,453 --> 00:04:05,871
<font face="Serif" size="18">See, you love doing that.</font>

59
00:04:05,954 --> 00:04:08,290
<font face="Serif" size="18">And we love helping new life-forms
get their footing.</font>

60
00:04:08,373 --> 00:04:12,586
<font face="Serif" size="18">So now that we're back,
we can respectfully take it from here.</font>

61
00:04:12,669 --> 00:04:15,756
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now, hold on. if you've seen <i>Endgame,
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">you know invasion is not something</font>

62
00:04:15,839 --> 00:04:16,923
<font face="Serif" size="18">Earth takes lying down.</font>

63
00:04:17,007 --> 00:04:21,762
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is not an invasion.
Besides, wouldn't you like to lie down?</font>

64
00:04:21,845 --> 00:04:23,847
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh. You must be exhausted.</font>

65
00:04:23,930 --> 00:04:28,477
<font face="Serif" size="18">Put your feet up, get more tattoos,
finish rounding out this Ant-Man character.</font>

66
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:31,855
<font face="Serif" size="18">Think of it like your Earth concept of "vacation,"
except permanent.</font>

67
00:04:31,938 --> 00:04:34,316
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think I speak for all world leaders
when I say that</font>

68
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:37,652
<font face="Serif" size="18">the poor people would just murder us
if we made you leave, so...</font>

69
00:04:37,736 --> 00:04:38,945
<font face="Serif" size="18">[clears throat]</font>

70
00:04:39,446 --> 00:04:41,323
<font face="Serif" size="18">Welcome home, dinosaurs.</font>

71
00:04:41,406 --> 00:04:42,991
<font face="Serif" size="18">[man] Oh. I could use a vacation.</font>

72
00:04:43,074 --> 00:04:45,327
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Should we nuke them?
- I'm on vacation, Curtis.</font>

73
00:04:45,410 --> 00:04:47,245
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, you leaned into this fast.</font>

74
00:04:47,329 --> 00:04:48,872
<font face="Serif" size="18">[rock music playing]</font>

75
00:04:48,955 --> 00:04:52,751
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Zuniceratops</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

76
00:04:52,834 --> 00:04:56,463
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Elvisaurus</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

77
00:04:56,546 --> 00:04:58,882
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Bambiraptor</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

78
00:04:58,965 --> 00:05:01,009
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Erectopus</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

79
00:05:01,092 --> 00:05:05,764
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Dracorex Hogwartsia</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

80
00:05:05,847 --> 00:05:09,184
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Gojirasaurus</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

81
00:05:09,267 --> 00:05:11,144
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Vulcanodon</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

82
00:05:11,228 --> 00:05:13,146
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Sauroniops</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

83
00:05:13,230 --> 00:05:16,942
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Phuwiangosaurus</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

84
00:05:17,025 --> 00:05:21,279
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Those are real dinosaur names</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

85
00:05:21,363 --> 00:05:22,572
<font face="Serif" size="18">[groans]</font>

86
00:05:23,615 --> 00:05:24,741
<font face="Serif" size="18">[alarm buzzing]</font>

87
00:05:27,035 --> 00:05:31,248
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't even pretend to feel useful in a game.
This is how humanity's story ends?</font>

88
00:05:31,331 --> 00:05:33,542
<font face="Serif" size="18">Relieved of duty and sat at the kid's table?</font>

89
00:05:33,625 --> 00:05:35,126
<font face="Serif" size="18">I got to respect these dinosaurs.</font>

90
00:05:35,210 --> 00:05:38,922
<font face="Serif" size="18">They dominated a whole species just by calling
its bluff about wanting more free time.</font>

91
00:05:39,005 --> 00:05:41,508
<font face="Serif" size="18">They didn't dominate us
because we're not worth a fight.</font>

92
00:05:41,591 --> 00:05:43,426
<font face="Serif" size="18">We've become biological Tyler Perry movies.</font>

93
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:45,762
<font face="Serif" size="18">- All they've done is help.
- We didn't need their help.</font>

94
00:05:45,846 --> 00:05:47,806
<font face="Serif" size="18">We were not the problem. This house recycles.</font>

95
00:05:49,349 --> 00:05:52,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">They sort it at the trash facility.</font>

96
00:05:52,143 --> 00:05:55,272
<font face="Serif" size="18">What the eff? My dance videos
are getting zero likes now.</font>

97
00:05:55,355 --> 00:05:59,276
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Oh, yeah. The dinos kicked pedophiles off TikTok.
- Great. So now I'm broke?</font>

98
00:05:59,359 --> 00:06:03,154
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You don't need money anymore.
- So what's this for now? Phone calls? Ugh.</font>

99
00:06:03,238 --> 00:06:05,115
<font face="Serif" size="18">Come on, Dad. You don't hate this too?</font>

100
00:06:05,198 --> 00:06:07,409
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why would I? I was already doing what I wanted.</font>

101
00:06:07,492 --> 00:06:10,537
<font face="Serif" size="18">I do think it's kind of funny
that you're all basically Jerry now.</font>

102
00:06:11,121 --> 00:06:12,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fuck.</font>

103
00:06:12,831 --> 00:06:14,583
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jerry, how do you do it?</font>

104
00:06:14,666 --> 00:06:17,294
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Yeah, Dad, how do you do it?
- How do you do it, Dad?</font>

105
00:06:17,377 --> 00:06:19,379
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Huh?
- [all] How do you do it?</font>

106
00:06:19,462 --> 00:06:21,256
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's finally happened.</font>

107
00:06:36,187 --> 00:06:37,355
<font face="Serif" size="18">[laughs]</font>

108
00:06:37,439 --> 00:06:39,024
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right.</font>

109
00:06:39,107 --> 00:06:42,527
<font face="Serif" size="18">Does anyone know how to mail things
to publishers?</font>

110
00:06:42,611 --> 00:06:43,486
<font face="Serif" size="18">[phone chiming]</font>

111
00:06:43,570 --> 00:06:47,032
<font face="Serif" size="18">President only pages me if it's an emergency
or he needs Molly.</font>

112
00:06:51,119 --> 00:06:55,790
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm sure glad you stayed open, Beau.
Wish we could pay, but no more capitalism.</font>

113
00:06:56,374 --> 00:06:59,169
<font face="Serif" size="18">I never make ribs for the money, Mr. President.</font>

114
00:06:59,252 --> 00:07:01,463
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, here you go.</font>

115
00:07:01,546 --> 00:07:04,424
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's not why I called.
Drugs can't solve this problem.</font>

116
00:07:04,507 --> 00:07:06,051
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't live like this anymore.</font>

117
00:07:06,134 --> 00:07:09,596
<font face="Serif" size="18">At first, it was fun spending all day watching
whatever YouTube autoplays</font>

118
00:07:09,679 --> 00:07:13,099
<font face="Serif" size="18">after the last one autoplayed, but a man
can only watch so many ads for Grammarly.</font>

119
00:07:13,183 --> 00:07:17,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick. Please. You're not bound by morality.
Get rid of them. Slit their necks.</font>

120
00:07:17,604 --> 00:07:20,065
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Zero Dark Thirty</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> these fuckers
for the good of the species.</font>

121
00:07:20,148 --> 00:07:24,069
<font face="Serif" size="18">I won't tell. Help us go back to the old days,
where we pretend to fix the problems we caused.</font>

122
00:07:24,152 --> 00:07:27,030
<font face="Serif" size="18">You think I'm going to side with you
over hyper-intelligent creatures</font>

123
00:07:27,113 --> 00:07:30,533
<font face="Serif" size="18">operating way beyond your comprehension?
I have more in common with them than you.</font>

124
00:07:30,617 --> 00:07:33,662
<font face="Serif" size="18">You pompous autistic cadaver!
You think you're above this?</font>

125
00:07:33,745 --> 00:07:35,413
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I ought to--
- Look here, Mr. President.</font>

126
00:07:35,497 --> 00:07:39,167
<font face="Serif" size="18">When I need my ribs to be tender and delicious,
I pamper them.</font>

127
00:07:39,250 --> 00:07:44,130
<font face="Serif" size="18">See, if you give someone what they want,
they'll give you what you need.</font>

128
00:07:44,214 --> 00:07:46,466
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I'm just saying.
- I see your point, Beau.</font>

129
00:07:46,549 --> 00:07:49,135
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right, Rick. Name your price.</font>

130
00:07:49,970 --> 00:07:51,680
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Oh, crap.
- Goddamn it!</font>

131
00:07:51,763 --> 00:07:56,768
<font face="Serif" size="18">- How often are you <i>Westworld</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">-ing me?
- Hang on. Rib-tips jammed his folk-chip again.</font>

132
00:07:56,851 --> 00:08:00,313
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ol' reliable Rick. Always knows what to do.</font>

133
00:08:00,397 --> 00:08:01,398
<font face="Serif" size="18">What do you want, Rick?</font>

134
00:08:01,481 --> 00:08:04,317
<font face="Serif" size="18">I won't stoop to answering that again.
You know exactly what I want.</font>

135
00:08:04,401 --> 00:08:06,486
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't snap my fingers and get you that job.</font>

136
00:08:06,569 --> 00:08:09,114
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Yeah, yeah. Thanks for lunch.
- Fine. Fine!</font>

137
00:08:09,197 --> 00:08:12,117
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you get rid of the dinosaurs,
you can host the Oscars.</font>

138
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,034
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes!</font>

139
00:08:13,118 --> 00:08:18,415
<font face="Serif" size="18">Righteous Rick. Straight shooting, truth-telling,
never wets the bed.</font>

140
00:08:21,001 --> 00:08:26,089
<font face="Serif" size="18">Goodbye, old friends. May you rest in peace,
rather than the tank of an SUV.</font>

141
00:08:26,172 --> 00:08:28,883
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hello, fellow cosmic voyagers.</font>

142
00:08:28,967 --> 00:08:30,010
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can we help you?</font>

143
00:08:30,093 --> 00:08:31,886
<font face="Serif" size="18">Actually, I can probably help you.</font>

144
00:08:31,970 --> 00:08:35,640
<font face="Serif" size="18">See, I'm technically human, but I've come
to be more, you know, on your level.</font>

145
00:08:35,724 --> 00:08:36,933
<font face="Serif" size="18">We're fine, thank you.</font>

146
00:08:37,017 --> 00:08:38,268
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe I'm being too indirect.</font>

147
00:08:38,351 --> 00:08:40,353
<font face="Serif" size="18">I happen to dabble in multiversal travel,</font>

148
00:08:40,437 --> 00:08:42,772
<font face="Serif" size="18">and I could probably zap you guys
to an alternate Earth.</font>

149
00:08:42,856 --> 00:08:46,276
<font face="Serif" size="18">We used portal travel eons ago,
but evolved to a one-universe,</font>

150
00:08:46,359 --> 00:08:49,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">one-truth policy
as the highest form of existence.</font>

151
00:08:49,404 --> 00:08:53,533
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sort of a "put your own oxygen mask on
before helping others" type of a thing.</font>

152
00:08:53,616 --> 00:08:55,160
<font face="Serif" size="18">Have you been on a plane?</font>

153
00:08:55,243 --> 00:08:56,828
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes, I've been on a plane.</font>

154
00:08:56,911 --> 00:08:59,748
<font face="Serif" size="18">We have no problem if you jump dimensions.</font>

155
00:08:59,831 --> 00:09:02,459
<font face="Serif" size="18">Although we sense
your gateway device is suboptimal.</font>

156
00:09:02,542 --> 00:09:03,376
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let us help.</font>

157
00:09:03,460 --> 00:09:05,837
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't need help. I'm here to help you.</font>

158
00:09:06,504 --> 00:09:07,464
<font face="Serif" size="18">What the hell is this?</font>

159
00:09:07,547 --> 00:09:11,301
<font face="Serif" size="18">A Portal Pistol. The gateways are see-through,
not a green swirl,</font>

160
00:09:11,384 --> 00:09:13,261
<font face="Serif" size="18">so now you can see where you're going.</font>

161
00:09:13,344 --> 00:09:14,262
<font face="Serif" size="18">Clever girl.</font>

162
00:09:14,345 --> 00:09:17,348
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you'd like, we could patch up your little
interdimensional rift too.</font>

163
00:09:17,432 --> 00:09:21,102
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, leave it. I know how to close that.
That's there for a reason. Very canonical.</font>

164
00:09:21,186 --> 00:09:23,813
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Don't you just want it closed?
